name: Slurty3
description: Slurty3 is a indica-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Slurricane and Gelato 33. Bred by Purple City Genetics, Slurty3 is 19% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Slurty3 effects make them feel talkative, giggly, and happy. Medical marijuana patients often choose Slurty3 when dealing with symptoms associated with pain, stress, and depression. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is caryophyllene. Slurty3 features an aroma and flavor profile of sweet, earthy, and floral.
